name: AstroDonkey
description: What is AstroDonkey? Experts advise to invest in strong Development teams. That's why we formed an LLC business, spent 8 months creating a master plan, and launched the central token of our new ecosystem called AstroDonkey ($DNKY). The four DEVs are experienced, over-doxxed, and based in the USA. Not only are our identities public knowledge, we are available to discuss the project with investors every day in our telegram. This ground-breaking ecosystem delivers Auto-LP, Auto-Burn, a community governed wallet with monthly voting, an NFT marketplace, fundraising for schools, monthly charitable contributions, purely organic growth, and proprietary crypto applications that will be releasing in the very near future. Through hard work, integrity, and no days off, this Development team will raise the standard of crypto projects for years to come. It is not just a token, it's a company. This is only the beginning.
